  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd 4 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u00a0\u0b9a\u0bbf.\u0b90.\u0b9f\u0bbf. \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The CID spent 4 hours with journalist Tarindu. Investigation",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The CID's Computer Crimes Investigation Division summoned journalist Darindu Uduwarakethara today (28) and interrogated him for about 4 hours and recorded his vote.",
        "The inquiries were conducted following a complaint lodged by the Air Force Intelligence on September 6, last year (2021), alleging that the title and content of the videos uploaded to the YouTube channel 'Sattana' conducted by the journalist were inconsistent.",
        "During the investigation it was pointed out that there were videos of color criticizing the government and one was obtained by ballot.",
        "At 9.00 am today, in the presence of Sub-Inspector Madushanka of the CID's Computer Crime Investigation Room, journalist Darindu Uduwaragedara was interrogated until one o'clock in the afternoon.",
        "Journalists and social activists staged a peaceful demonstration in front of the CID, urging freedom of expression and freedom of the press.",
        "C.I.T. Lawyer Prabodha Ratnayake appeared before the CID along with journalist Darindu Uduwarakethara during the interrogation."
      ],
